query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 b q1 s t1 tq1 u1) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from tag_question AS tq1
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.score >= 0 AND q1.score <= 5
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('math')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('banach-spaces',
'convergence',
'geometry',
'indefinite-integrals',
'lebesgue-integral',
'number-theory',
'self-learning',
'sobolev-spaces')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name IN ('Commentator',
'Editor',
'Famous Question',
'Peer Pressure',
'Promoter',
'Supporter',
'Teacher',
'Yearling')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND u1.upvotes >= 0 AND u1.upvotes <= 100
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
